{"tid":310023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「研究」 射精有助防脫髮","createTime":"2017-07-05T13:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T14:54:34.000Z","uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a79bf291d0c4b1870aab823efacc8a8c90d3002","tid":310023,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:12:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/health/q2aejo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhealth%2Fq2aejo.html&d=H%2BmGSSDlm%2F1MMi2VZFfN66WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d96f8bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/health/q2aejo.html</a><br />\n健康科普：多做愛可以防止脫髮<br />\n<br />\n多射精對頭髮健康有利<br />\n<br />\n話分兩頭，先說脫髮的原因。現代醫學認為，由睪丸所製造出來的睪酮，會隨著血液循環到達頭髮的毛囊細胞，通過細胞膜進入細胞質。細胞內有5a-還原酶，會催化睪酮，使之轉化雙氫睪酮，雙氫睪酮進入細胞核，對於代謝系統造成影響，會阻礙其能量物質的製造而受阻。進而使得毛髮蛋白合成受阻，毛母細胞失去活力，開始角質化，最終成為休止期毛髮。而進入休止期的毛髮，因缺乏養分，大約3個月內就會脫落。因此講，<span style=\"color: red;\">雙氫睪酮的作用就是毒害毛囊，抑制頭髮的生長。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/9df0007c6a829c9d16e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F9df0007c6a829c9d16e&h=f7dc9b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外一方面，<span style=\"color: red;\">當人在射精的時候會將睪丸激素轉化為雙氫睪酮，射出體內。</span>因為，睪酮可直接或先轉變為活性更強的雙氫睪酮，與生精細胞的雄激素受體結合，促進精子的生成。而射精，就會減少雙氫睪酮在體內的含量。而上文已經介紹，脫髮的原因是體內的雙氫睪酮較多，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以做愛從本質上來說，可以防止脫髮。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>以下係現實例子：</ins></span>"},{"pid":"18a87fe0f71b9871dd28f57461b230ec58000dd9","tid":310023,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32a78b49e20259511c59289bb3ab0c9ba0e28be7","tid":310023,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁女人脫髮點算</blockquote><br />\n潮吹囉"},{"pid":"e6eb32fe8cb3292498e7389bdefd1a07eefb7416","tid":310023,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:17:07.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 阿諾舒華辛力加</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n「阿諾有很強的性需要，他相信勤做愛會令他結實，<span style=\"color: red;\">他每一日做五次</span>，還指五字好意頭！」(Source: 東方, <a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20131017/00288_009.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20131017%2F00288_009.html&d=H%2BmGSSDlm%2F1MMi2VZFfN66WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=76b70271\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20131017/00288_009.html</a>) <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/28dg23a34do/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F28dg23a34do%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=160d8a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1： 阿諾69歲都頭髮量極多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 秋官</span></ins><br />\n<img src=\"http://photocdn.sohu.com/20080221/Img255286744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotocdn.sohu.com%2F20080221%2FImg255286744.jpg&h=41f211e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2：秋官配偶為肥姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/106d0002c00f485411a5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F106d0002c00f485411a5&h=93e4c151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖3：男人最痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a629ee88afd4b3fa6fdafed10050dd5ed47d29a","tid":310023,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:27:32.000Z","msg":"屌你秋官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ec9b360409c0f57f8acf45d63d36ff241242d2","tid":310023,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"蕭別離唔係咁講嫁啵<br />\n蕭生出黎面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cf0def0ff86bda463f8f0a54baac06f5aab4df","tid":310023,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20